<b>Directed Actions:</b>
<b>open/close:</b> open or close a door
<b>lock/unlock:</b> lock or unlock a closed door
<b>pick:</b> pick a locked door (try to, anyway)
<b>ask (not) follow:</b> ask an NPC to follow you (or not)
<b>ask (not) not move:</b> ask an NPC to not move (to stay where they are, in other words) (or not)
<b>attack:</b> attack something (typically a lifeform, like a zombie or NPC human, or, an inanimate but destructible object, like a window or closed door)
